# Build artefacts (anywhere in the tree).
*.agdai
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*~

# Documentation / handoff notes are kept locally but not tracked.
*.md

# Whitelist policy: only the following files/dirs are tracked.
#   /BRA/            -- the active Agda codebase (incl. BRA/godelI-II-summary.pdf)
#   /bra-godelII.tex -- the project paper / writeup
#
# Everything else (including CLAUDE.md, README.md, root-level reference
# PDFs, build artefacts, and /old/ which holds the prior frozen state)
# is untracked.

/*

!/.gitignore
!/BRA/
!/bra-godelII.tex
